1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,720
- Oh, right! Next time, we... 
 - Sungwoo.

2
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,600
Why do you like me?

3
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,880
♫ <i>I was preparing myself for us to part</i> ♫

4
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:13,400
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

5
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:18,490
<i> [Episode 11] 
 [Why You Should Hide Your Crush]</i>

6
00:00:18,490 --> 00:00:22,280
♫ <i>I stay up all night thinking about us</i> ♫

7
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:33,760
What's all this? Are you going to remodel the shop again?

8
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:36,280
No, I just cleaned.

9
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:38,040
That's my job.

10
00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:41,019
I need to get used not to having a part-timer now.

11
00:00:41,019 --> 00:00:42,860
Our contract will be expired soon.

12
00:00:42,860 --> 00:00:45,940
You're right. It'll be spring soon.

13
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:47,860
It was really long.

14
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:52,100
It was midsummer when you first came here.

15
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:54,480
Time does fly.

16
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:04,100
- I should move this to the warehouse, right? 
 - Put it down and just come here.

17
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:08,680
Why?

18
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,280
<i>[Magic Insurance Contract]</i>

19
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:13,700
I want to give you a present to celebrate the end of your contract.

20
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,480
No, I won't use it.

21
00:01:17,580 --> 00:01:19,500
You still can't trust me?

22
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,640
Just take a look first.

23
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,380
What's this?

24
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:28,420
It's an insurance contract.

25
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:31,220
It's a magic insurance contract to be exact.

26
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,800
- I won't do it. 
 - Just read it.

27
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:38,780
I'm just trying to make sure my magic can help you if something bad happens.

28
00:01:38,780 --> 00:01:41,160
Why are you doing this out of the blue?

29
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:44,840
Because you make me feel so worried whatever you do.

30
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,296
You're the same way.

31
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:52,160
Anyways, it's for you. So, take a close look.

32
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:57,460
It doesn't look right either.

33
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:11,760
- Youngji, eat this. 
 - Thanks.

34
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:17,480
- What's the matter? 
 - What?

35
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:20,880
Your response is different from usual.

36
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,980
It's nothing.

37
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:25,820
Are you in the same class as me? You come to my class everyday.

38
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:28,340
I just stopped by.

39
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:30,500
Because I'm in the class next to yours.

40
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:36,340
By the way, do you have time after school?

41
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,960
Why?

42
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,580
I found a new restaurant.

43
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:43,060
Do you want to come with me after school?

44
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:46,080
- We might as well go there now. 
 - Now?

45
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,020
Why? You can't?

46
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:51,700
Well... Of course I can.

47
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:53,420
Let's go.

48
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,560
What are you doing? You're not going?

49
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:09,500
- Hey, Youngji. 
 - Yeah?

50
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:14,340
As we're skipping our class, we might as well jump over a wall.

51
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:15,040
What?

52
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:17,280
Where are you going? You should be in class now.

53
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,870
Sir, we...

54
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:21,570
We have to go out.

55
00:03:21,579 --> 00:03:22,850
We can't?

56
00:03:22,850 --> 00:03:24,320
What are you talking about?

57
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:27,220
You should be in class of course.

58
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:33,179
But you can go out to play. Sure. That's how you grow.

59
00:03:33,179 --> 00:03:34,220
What?

60
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:37,690
Since you're already going out, you'd better make sure you have fun.

61
00:03:37,699 --> 00:03:39,560
Yes, Sir.

62
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:43,140
Good bye, Sir.

63
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,780
By the way, where are we going?

64
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:46,580
Just come.

65
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,700
I've been wanting to come here.

66
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,880
Hyeji said it's really beautiful.

67
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:57,000
True. It's so beautiful.

68
00:03:57,540 --> 00:04:00,440
I thought I should come here someday.

69
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,396
Now I'm here.

70
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:04,340
Thanks to you.

71
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:08,600
You don't have to thank me. You brought me here. I should thank you.

72
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:11,300
Is it because everybody is at school?

73
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,140
It's so quiet.

74
00:04:13,140 --> 00:04:14,980
I know, right.

75
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:18,860
I like that it's so quiet.

76
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:23,500
Youngji, would you go stand over there?

77
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,620
I'll take a photo of you.

78
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:29,520
Forget it. I don't take pictures.

79
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,080
Then, shall we take a picture together?

80
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,340
It's a cafe street. Isn't it beautiful?

81
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:36,000
- Excuse me. 
 - Yes.

82
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:39,180
I'm sorry but can you take a photo of us, please?

83
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:41,340
- You two... 
 - Yes.

84
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,839
You must be a couple like us.

85
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:47,660
- No, we're not. Sure, I'll do it. 
 - Thank you.

86
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:57,899
You look a bit awkward. Please stand closer to each other.

87
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:59,660
Like us.

88
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:05,620
Good, good. Smile big.

89
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:07,640
Here we go.

90
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:10,460
One, two, three.

91
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,959
Maybe we shouldn't have taken a photo.

92
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:19,080
- Still, we came out well. 
 - Really?

93
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:22,080
- I'll send it to you later. 
 - Sure.

94
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:25,680
What?

95
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,820
I want to go there.

96
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:30,460
Sure. Let's go.

97
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:37,100
Wow. It's amazing.

98
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:39,460
I've never done this before.

99
00:05:39,460 --> 00:05:42,520
You can play it even if it's your first time. Let's play it together.

100
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,880
Sure. Let's give it a try.

101
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:48,180
♫ <i> Yeah. Swag </i> ♫

102
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:49,430
I'm the blue one.

103
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:52,000
♫ <i> Eeny, miny, moe </i> ♫

104
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:55,690
♫ <i> Time out! That's cheating. I almost fell for your tricks </i> ♫

105
00:05:55,690 --> 00:05:58,840
♫ <i> You were too late. We have to redo it </i> ♫

106
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:02,930
♫ <i> Why are you denying it with you're catlike eyes? </i> ♫

107
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,740
♫ <i> I'll let you off easy today </i> ♫

108
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,920
Why do you keep dying?

109
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:18,340
- It's your first time, right? 
 - Yes.

110
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:23,319
Huh? Let's play that, too. That's totally my style.

111
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:25,960
Sure. Let's play that, too.

112
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:30,820
♫ <i> Don't cross the line, I'm still young </i> ♫

113
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:33,500
♫ <i> Stop! Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

114
00:06:35,410 --> 00:06:39,430
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited until you apologize </i> ♫

115
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:41,560
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited. Approaching is prohibited now </i> ♫

116
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:46,260
It's weird today.

117
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:50,800
What? It's too easy. No fun.

118
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,200
Do you want me to pick up a doll for you?

119
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,640
No, I'm fine.

120
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:58,100
Why? I'm really good at it.

121
00:06:58,100 --> 00:07:00,356
Do you even know how to play it?

122
00:07:00,380 --> 00:07:01,980
Of... Of course.

123
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:07,360
I used to pick out two dolls at a time.

124
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,460
I felt really sorry for the owner.

125
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:12,850
Wait. I'll get a doll for you.

126
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:16,400
♫ <i> S.O.S yo. Be careful of</i> ♫

127
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,240
♫ <i> Dracula's teeth and broken glass </i> ♫

128
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:21,360
♫ <i> My sharp mood is the 8th wonder of the world </i> ♫

129
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:25,000
♫ <i> I really like you, but I've turned my back to you </i> ♫

130
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:28,860
♫ <i> I just want you to approach me first </i> ♫

131
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:32,120
♫ <i> You keep your poker face no matter how sad 
 my voice is when I talk </i> ♫

132
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,500
♫ <i> Your like an unblinking ice princess </i> ♫

133
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,210
I have more chances left.

134
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:39,290
Hey, get out of the way.

135
00:07:39,290 --> 00:07:43,500
♫ <i> Don't cross the line, I'm still young </i> ♫

136
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:47,960
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

137
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:50,380
Here, you take it.

138
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:54,120
Really? Thanks.

139
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,899
I'm hungry.

140
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:58,290
Let's go eat.

141
00:07:58,290 --> 00:08:01,360
♫ <i> Until. Until you say sorry </i> ♫

142
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:06,280
Wait for me. Wait, I'll take your bag.

143
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:18,280
You must really like tteokbokki.

144
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,910
Yeah,

145
00:08:19,910 --> 00:08:25,010
I think tteokbokki is the most perfect food in this world.

146
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,416
It's a perfect combination of sweetness and saltiness.

147
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:29,640
How can it taste like this?

148
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,060
But you know what?

149
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:34,380
The first food that we ate together was also tteokbokki.

150
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:39,780
Was it? I can't remember, since I ate so many things with you.

151
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:45,480
Really? I remember everything though.

152
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:54,720
- Do you want to order more? 
 - No.

153
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,540
I'm full.

154
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,680
Oh, okay.

155
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:07,700
- Aren't you eating? 
 - Oh, I should eat.

156
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,479
It's cold at night.

157
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:16,616
- Right? 
 - Yeah.

158
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,300
How was today's tteokbokki?

159
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,620
Is it worthy of being on your list of delicious places?

160
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:25,580
Well, it was not bad.

161
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:29,080
- Right, next time we... 
 - Sungwoo.

162
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,580
Why do you like me?

163
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,680
Well...

164
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,950
You already knew?

165
00:09:41,950 --> 00:09:45,060
♫ <i> Even easily said words </i> ♫

166
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:51,480
♫ <i> Even small actions </i> ♫

167
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,890
Sorry.

168
00:09:53,890 --> 00:09:57,000
♫ <i> Even if I can't say it </i> ♫

169
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:00,520
Youngji.

170
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:04,080
If you don't feel uncomfortable with me,

171
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,210
will you go to eat a delicious food with me later?

172
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:11,200
♫ <i> The shape of your back from far away </i> ♫

173
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:14,420
It's getting late.

174
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:18,480
I should go now.

175
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:22,720
<i> If I had taken courage and told her that I liked her earlier...</i>

176
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:27,820
<i> If I hadn't hesitated like this...</i>

177
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:30,260
Hey, Sungwoo.

178
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:33,820
Yeah?

179
00:10:33,820 --> 00:10:35,960
Thanks.

180
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,700
And...

181
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:42,910
I enjoyed the tteokbokki today.

182
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:50,300
♫ <i> How much more do I need to be right in front 
 of you before you recognize me?</i> ♫

183
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:52,640
See you at school tomorrow.

184
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:55,980
And I know many more places that sell better tteokbokki.

185
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:58,490
Let's go together later.

186
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:05,090
<i>[A Good Luck Insurance Contract] </i>

187
00:11:05,090 --> 00:11:07,240
<i>[Closed]</i>

188
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,290
<i>[Closed | See you again]</i>

189
00:11:09,290 --> 00:11:12,890
♫ <i> The closer I get, the more scared I am </i> ♫

190
00:11:12,890 --> 00:11:18,890
♫ <i> That you'll move away. So, I stay still </i> ♫

191
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:24,990
♫ <i> Without saying anything </i> ♫
